{"type":null,"faqId":17880,"title":"为什么通话时，手机贴近耳部时屏幕会自动关闭，离开后仍然为黑屏？","answer":"<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">手机屏幕上方靠近听筒的位置内置有接近光传感器。</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">在通话过程中，手机贴近耳部或有其他物体遮挡住上方的屏幕时，手机会自动关闭屏幕，离开遮挡物后屏幕会自动点亮方便您操作。</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt;\">若在通话过程中，手机离开耳部仍然为黑屏，请检查上方的屏幕是否被遮挡。</span><br>\n<img border=\"0\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20150104111036856001.png\" style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 12pt; width: 36.75pt; height: 12pt;\">\n<div><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; line-height: 10pt;\">为了保证您的正常使用，请注意不要用手机套或其他物体遮挡听筒及其附近的屏幕。使用屏幕保护膜时，也请勿遮盖感应器部位，建议您购买本手机专用屏幕保护膜。</span><br>\n<p>\n<br>\n</p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"640","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1420341050000,"seriesProductName":"SC-CL00","visitedTimes":152,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}